{"id":757015,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Othon_Bastos","text":"Othon Bastos (born 23 May 1933) is a Brazilian movie actor. He has appeared in 50 movies since 1962. He was born in Tucano, Bahia.\nHis best known roles were in \"O Pagador de Promessas\" (1962), \"Black God, White Devil\" (1964), \"Antonio das Mortes\" (1969), \"Of Gods and the Undead\" (1970), \"S. Bernardo\" (1972), \"The Last Plantation\" (1976), \"Heart and Guts\" (1982), \"Four Days in September\" (1997), \"Central Station\" (1998), \"Villa-Lobos - Uma Vida de Paix\u00E3o\" (2000), \"Behind the Sun\" (2001), \"Nosso Lar\" (2010) and \"Os Experientes\" (2016).","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"Tucano%2C_Bahia","surface_form":"Tucano","offset":116},{"uri":"Bahia","surface_form":"Bahia","offset":124},{"uri":"O_Pagador_de_Promessas","surface_form":"O Pagador de Promessas","offset":161},{"uri":"Black_God%2C_White_Devil","surface_form":"Black God, White Devil","offset":194},{"uri":"Antonio_das_Mortes","surface_form":"Antonio das Mortes","offset":227},{"uri":"Of_Gods_and_the_Undead","surface_form":"Of Gods and the Undead","offset":256},{"uri":"S._Bernardo","surface_form":"S. Bernardo","offset":289},{"uri":"The_Last_Plantation","surface_form":"The Last Plantation","offset":311},{"uri":"Heart_and_Guts","surface_form":"Heart and Guts","offset":341},{"uri":"Four_Days_in_September","surface_form":"Four Days in September","offset":366},{"uri":"Central_Station","surface_form":"Central Station","offset":399},{"uri":"Villa-Lobos_-_Uma_Vida_de_Paix%C3%A3o","surface_form":"Villa-Lobos - Uma Vida de Paix\u00E3o","offset":425},{"uri":"Behind_the_Sun","surface_form":"Behind the Sun","offset":468},{"uri":"Nosso_Lar","surface_form":"Nosso Lar","offset":493},{"uri":"Os_Experientes","surface_form":"Os Experientes","offset":516}]}